select_entities.description:
Select which discovered ETA entities should be added to Home Assistant.

Sensors: {float_count}
Switches: {switch_count}
State sensors: {text_count}
Writable sensors: {writable_count}
**Total: {total_count}**

Enable auto-select-all if you want to add everything at once. On large systems this can create several hundred entities.

